com.mapbox.mapboxsdk.constants

Class Style

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mapbox.mapboxsdk.constants.Style

  • public class Style
extends java.lang.Object

    Style provides URLs to several professional styles designed by Mapbox.

    These styles are all ready to go in your app. To load one, pass it into MapView.setStyleUrl(String)
    See Also:
    MapView.setStyleUrl(String)

      • getMapboxStreetsUrl

        public static java.lang.String getMapboxStreetsUrl(int version)
        Get versioned url of Mapbox streets style.
        • Current default version is 9.

        More information on the Mapbox styles API can be found on https://www.mapbox.com/api-documentation/#styles

        Parameters:
        version - the version of the style.
        Returns:
        uri to load style from
